                            <i class="fas fa-dollar-sign"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Pricing Your Property</h3>
                        <p>Comprehensive guide to pricing strategies and market analysis for maximum returns.</p>
                        <div class="resource-meta">
                            <span class="resource-type">Strategy</span>
